See issue #136 

The one question I have here is the semantics around batching. In our implementation, we use block semantics (from clang), to batch looks like:

connection_batch(^{
    connection_send(...);
    connection_send(...);
});

where the block is called inline, and the batch is over when the block returns. I'm not sure what the right style for the pseudo-code is for the draft.
